description: Modern luxury meets seaside living at THE ICON! This luxurious, waterfront homes was built from the ground up by prominent developers with extreme attention to detail! The sprawling 2,400 sf floor-through residence features sweeping views of the coveted South Boston coastline, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a 2nd living room or 4th bedroom, private deck, private yard, 2 garage parking spaces and private elevator access. Artfully designed kitchens begin with oak & light gray cabinetry by Divine Design complemented by Quartz counters & backsplashes and designer Miele and Fisher Paykel appliances. The open concept living area features floor-to-ceiling Pella windows, wide oak flooring and flows onto a front facing deck with collapsible doors, and spiral staircase down to your private beach facing greenery. The primary suite showcases a pristine, spa-like bath with dual sinks, an oversized shower, a separate soaking tub & radiant floors. The ICON sets a new standard in South Boston!
